Project layout

trending-news/
│
├─ src/
│   ├─ fetch_trending.js          # main script (run by scheduler)
│   ├─ news_api.js                # thin wrapper around NewsAPI
│   ├─ scorer.js                  # simple trending‑score algorithm
│   ├─ seo_builder.js             # creates HTML + JSON‑LD
│   └─ publisher/
│        ├─ static_publisher.js   # writes markdown files for Hugo/Jekyll
│        └─ wp_publisher.js       # pushes via WP REST API
│
├─ .env                           # store API keys & config (do NOT commit)
├─ package.json
├─ Dockerfile
└─ README.md
